data.name: sqlDeleteCommand1.CommandText
data.value: DELETE FROM [AsfalticoMal] WHERE (([Folio] = @Original_Folio) AND ([Renglon] = @Original_Renglon) AND ((@IsNull_Malla = 1 AND [Malla] IS NULL) OR ([Malla] = @Original_Malla)) AND ((@IsNull_Linea1 = 1 AND [Linea1] IS NULL) OR ([Linea1] = @Original_Linea1)) AND ((@IsNull_Linea2 = 1 AND [Linea2] IS NULL) OR ([Linea2] = @Original_Linea2)) AND ((@IsNull_Quepasa = 1 AND [Quepasa] IS NULL) OR ([Quepasa] = @Original_Quepasa)) AND ((@IsNull_Proyecto = 1 AND [Proyecto] IS NULL) OR ([Proyecto] = @Original_Proyecto)) AND ((@IsNull_Designacion = 1 AND [Designacion] IS NULL) OR ([Designacion] = @Original_Designacion)))

data.name: sqlInsertCommand1.CommandText
data.value: INSERT INTO [AsfalticoMal] ([Folio], [Renglon], [Malla], [Linea1], [Linea2], [Quepasa], [Proyecto], [Designacion]) VALUES (@Folio, @Renglon, @Malla, @Linea1, @Linea2, @Quepasa, @Proyecto, @Designacion); SELECT Folio, Renglon, Malla, Linea1, Linea2, Quepasa, Proyecto, Designacion FROM AsfalticoMal WHERE (Folio = @Folio) AND (Renglon = @Renglon) ORDER BY Folio
